Vesting Schedule

Community Sale:
30% of tokens will be unlocked on the listing date (expected in Q4 2025), and the remaining tokens will be unlocked linearly over the next 12 months.

Team & Angel Investor:
10% of tokens will be unlocked on the listing date, and the remaining tokens will be unlocked linearly over the next 120 months.

Foundation:
30% of tokens will be unlocked on the listing date, and the remaining tokens will be unlocked linearly over the next 12 months.

Ecosystem & Community Rewards:
60% of tokens will be unlocked on the listing date, and the remaining 40% will be unlocked over the next 24 months.

Stage #1
Research & Development
Goal: Platform preparation and Presale launch
  • Market and competitor analysis
  • Development of platform concept and tokenomics
  • Preparation of technical documentation (Whitepaper)🚀
  • Creation of app architecture and smart contracts
  • Pitsnap Trademark Registration ®
  • Website launch and marketing campaign
  • Community and partner network formation
  • Start of app development
  • Result: Basic infrastructure is ready
Stage #2
MVP Release
Goal: Launch of the Minimum Viable Product (MVP)
  • User registration and authentication
  • Content upload and viewing
  • Creator dashboard with analytics
  • Live streaming and broadcasts
  • Payment system integration
  • Crypto wallet integration and token payments
  • Basic smart contract implementation
  • Internal and closed beta testing
  • Result: MVP with core features released
Stage #3
Beta Version & Community Growth
Goal: Feature expansion and user engagement
  • UX/UI improvements
  • Smart contract optimization and security enhancements
  • Rating and comment system
  • User reward system
  • Decentralized marketplace for content and services
  • Blockchain-based ticket sales for concerts and events
  • Public beta testing
  • $PITS Token Listing on Major CEX Crypto Exchanges 🚀
  • Result: Beta version launched, token listed on exchanges
Stage #4
Market Expansion & Decentralization
Goal: Scaling and decentralization
  • Support for multiple cryptocurrencies and P2P transactions
  • NFT integration for unique content
  • Ecosystem expansion via developers and community
  • International localization
  • Partnerships with major content platforms
  • DAO launch for project governance
  • Continuous platform improvement and scaling
  • Result: Decentralized and scalable ecosystem
